  }), "Toastmasters"), " club officers. Organizing a speaker meeting for 15 people is one thing, but a virtual event with 120 participants who participate in various workshops in parallel brings several new challenges. And these need to be addressed. Let\u2019s see how the organizers did it."), mdx("h2", {
