    parentName: "div"
  }, "Image by Shahid Abdullah on Pixabay")), mdx("p", null, "One of the officers of the Levice club is preparing a unifying PR strategy and wants to start building awareness of Toastmasters in Slovakia as a whole. Today, when you type \u201Cpublic speaking\u201D into a search engine, you will find everything, except our clubs. And you know what they say, \u201CIf you\u2019re not on the first page of Google, it\u2019s like you don\u2019t exist.\u201D"), mdx("blockquote", null, mdx("p", {
    parentName: "blockquote"
  }, "Missed opportunity.")), mdx("p", null, "The lecture had no clear concept and seemed chaotic. Let\u2019s say that the speaker has no experience with speaking, but even then, I would expect her to provide us at least with valuable content. In that case, I would overlook the mistakes in the presentation."), mdx("p", null, "Here are my main observations (for some, I thank a few other participants):"), mdx("ul", null, mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
  }, "Information was too general, not at all related to building the Toastmasters brand in Slovakia"), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
  }, "Either the trainer didn\u2019t have enough know-how or didn\u2019t want to share it with us"), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
  }, "Misleading topic name. I would probably call it simply \u201CBranding\u201D"), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
  }, "No specific advice on how to effectively improve PR of clubs"), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
  }, "The problems were named, but the solutions were not. Example: When people type \u201Cpublic speaking\u201D into a search engine, they won\u2019t find you. The solution? Hire an SEO expert. Thanks for the advice; I already knew that"), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
  }, "She chaotically mentioned several social networks, even completely irrelevant to us. ", mdx("a", _extends({
