  }, {
    "href": "https://pinterest.com",
    "target": "_blank",
    "rel": "noreferrer"
  }), "Pinterest"), " isn\u2019t used by our target audience at all. Conversely, ", mdx("a", _extends({
    parentName: "li"
  }, {
    "href": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/23720854",
    "target": "_blank",
    "rel": "noreferrer"
  }), "LinkedIn"), " was mentioned only in connection with the fact that it is good to have a profile there. It is in LinkedIn that I see a huge potential for expanding the membership base"), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
  }, mdx("strong", {
    parentName: "li"
  }, "She didn\u2019t mention analytics at all"), ". If I followed her advice, I\u2019d make random erratic posts and see what happens. It\u2019s the ability to analyze data that is one of the most important in building PR"), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
  }, "She talked in depth about things we could read from slides. By the way, the fact that there is a lot of information on the slide is also bad. But I will talk about the correct presentation some other time"), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
  }, "The presentation contained errors. The word \u201CAlgorythm\u201D could not be overlooked. In copywriting training, I already learned how important it is to have proper grammar. Someone involved in marketing should know this. And if they don\u2019t check what they write after themselves, it seems amateurish and sloppy"), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
  }, "At the end, the presenter asked the marketer to close the presentation quickly because her time was up. She had the most time and still couldn\u2019t talk about the essentials")), mdx("p", null, "I have written many more of these shortcomings. I think everything I have mentioned here could be summed up in one sentence."), mdx("blockquote", null, mdx("p", {
    parentName: "blockquote"
  }, "Know your audience.")), mdx("p", null, "That is the exact name of one of the projects that some of us at Toastmasters have completed. The goal is to find out as much information as possible about your audience \u2014 their age, experience, what PR practices they would need to apply in their clubs, and so on."), mdx("div", {
